stories.title: Younis and Malik take Pakistan home
stories.subTitle: Pakistan v Zimbabwe, Paktel Cup, 2nd match
stories.summary: A superb opening spell from Tinashe Panyangara raised visions of an upset, but Shoaib Malik and Younis Khan rallied to inspire a three-wicket victory for Pakistan in the second match of the Paktel Cup at the Arbab Niaz Stadium in Peshawar
